$v: Ukuseta Okwenziwa kwi-SIM kuyaqhubeka, nceda ungasicimi isixhobo okanye uyeke ukuqhagamshelana kwinethiwekhi.
I-Simcard ayifundwanga, nceda uphinde uzame ngelinye ixesha.
Cima uphinde ulayite ifowuni yakho ukuze utshintsho lwakho lusebenze.
Ifowuni yakho ingamiselwa ngokusekelwe kwikhadi lakho le-SIM. Khetha enye yezi profayile zilandelayo ukuze uqhubeke.
Inetwekhi ayikalungi okanye isilele ukuqhagamshela kwiseva.
Ifowuni yakho isetwe ngokuhambelana ne-SIM khadi yomboneleli nkonzo wakho. Cofa  KULUNGILE ukuphuma
